{Speech 35 Answer 36}{}{Me.}
{Speech 35 Answer Exit}{}{Mmmm. Ook? Bye bye Mommy.}
{Speech 36}{}{You sure do look as though you're a might confused. I hate to see a critter suffer. Want something to eat?}
