{Speech 38 Answer Exit}{}{Well.}
{Speech 39}{}{About the ghost? Sure, what's it?}
{Speech 39 Answer 40}{}{I thought that you may know something about ghosts. One of 'em is hanging out in some abandoned house. He looks like a hearless murderer! Do you know what could help to fight him?}
