{Speech 39 Answer 40***}{}{Leanna said that you may know something about ghosts. One of 'em is hanging out in some abandoned house. He looks like a hearless murderer! Do you know what could help to fight him?}
{Speech 39 Answer 40****}{}{Lara said that you may know something about ghosts. One of 'em is hanging out in some abandoned house. He looks like a hearless murderer! Do you know what could help to fight him?}
{Speech 39 Answer 40*****}{}{Fred said that you may know something about ghosts. One of 'em is hanging out in some abandoned house. He looks like a hearless murderer! Do you know what could help to fight him?}
